{"tid":708363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即時交通] 挖泥車疑撞塌「龍門架」，獅子山隧道出九龍全封","createTime":"2018-06-19T08:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T15:50:00.000Z","uid":35221,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"880d7994c4b4aa87dce1d273844c93944b1e9cb3","tid":708363,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_01p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_01p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=86492d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_02p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_02p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=de578441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_03p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_03p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=5f72e166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_04p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_04p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=6e6ad611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_05p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_05p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=ef4fb336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/photo/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_06p.jpg?20180619165251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001_06p.jpg%3F20180619165251&h=b7511a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獅子山隧道發生交通意外，今午4時許，獅子山隧道九龍出口，有掛上交通指示牌俗稱「龍門架」的支架倒塌，未知是否有人受傷。據悉，事發時一輛運載挖泥車的工程車行經，挖泥車疑撞到龍門架肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署宣布，因交通意外，獅子山隧道往九龍方向近隧道管道出口的全線現已封閉。上址實施單管雙程行車。現時上址交通繁忙。現時在獅子山隧道往九龍方向的車龍龍尾已到新田圍。<br />\n<br />\n根據政府網頁顯示，設置於公共道路的道路設施（如燈柱、欄杆或路牌等）為政府公物，一般轄屬路政署維修。在交通意外事故中，若涉及有道路設施因有關事故被損毀，政府可循普通法下的民事案侵權法，向事涉人士追討其損失。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，警務處負責交通意外的調查及檢控工作。路政署在收到警務處的調查報告後，會首先派員實地視察，以決定需要維修的範圍。當決定範圍後，路政署便會根據維修工程合約所列的費用來計算所需維修工程的成本，然後再加上其他費用如部門行政費用及申請挖掘准許証的費用，以得出向負責人要求賠償的金額；並會向負責人發出付款通知書追討賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://轉自on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%BD%89%E8%87%AAon.cc&d=kfGbL%2FOjNJwp4oeQaGZtPxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a7559fe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">轉自on.cc</a>東網<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fweather%2F20180619%2Fbkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001.html&d=kfGbL%2FOjNJwp4oeQaGZtPxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=671c9c00\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/weather/20180619/bkn-20180619162654159-0619_00942_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1f9afa7e969835f98805c0f90d6a16cd1e17b40c","tid":708363,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"之前東隧好似都試過一單<br />\n<br />\n屌, 係咪ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 架?"},{"pid":"a32e3d395dcd50040859cfe8bd4eb27a76da3f2f","tid":708363,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:0